        Smart Home.
        Intelligent Living.
      
SmartThings lets you easily control, monitor, and secure your home from anywhere in the world.









 
 
 






          Control and monitor
          your home from one
          simple app
        
Learn more











 
 



      Few smart home companies are doing it as well as SmartThings...
      Sam Frizell, Best Gadgets of 2014, TIME Magazine, November 2014

More reviews

 





Plays well with others
Once you have the SmartThings Hub and free app, you can add as many devices as you want to customize your smart home.

More compatible products




 
 


Discover the benefits














Rise and Shine





Rise and Shine
Coffee machine knows when you wake up and starts brewing



Set the Mood





Set the Mood
Connected speaker turns on your favorite playlist when you come home



Listen to Barkley





Listen to Barkley
Dog or cat reminds you to feed it before it’s hungry



Monitor Your Home





Monitor Your Home
Alerts notify you if dangerous or off-limit areas of your home are accessed










Manage Your Energy





Manage Your Energy
SmartThings and connected thermostats set the perfect temperature and save you money



Keep an Eye on Things





Keep an Eye on Things
SmartThings and Wi-Fi cameras send you photos when there’s unexpected movement



Receive Alerts





Receive Alerts
Windows and doors send you notifications if they open unexpectedly



Find Your Way Out





Find Your Way Out
Keys tell you where you left them inside your home



Conserve Electricity





Conserve Electricity
Lights turn on/off when people come and go



Secure Your Home





Secure Your Home
Door automatically unlocks when you arrive and locks when you leave



Stay Connected





Stay Connected
Door tells you when family and pets come and go










Keep Track of Pets





Keep Track of Pets
Yard tells you if Barkley leaves unexpectedly



Deter Intruders





Deter Intruders
Lights turn on to make it appear like you’re home when you’re not



Scare Burglars





Scare Burglars
Windows and door trigger a loud alarm and flashing lights if there’s unexpected entry



Light Your Way Home





Light Your Way Home
Outdoor lights brighten at night when you come home



Drive In, Drive Out





Drive In, Drive Out
Garage door automatically opens and closes as your car comes and goes
















